flowchart TD
    A[Student opens modules page] --> B[System filters modules by tier]
    B --> C[Student selects module]
    C --> D[System loads lesson list]
    D --> E[Student selects lesson]
    E --> F[Check tier and sequence access]
    F --> G{Lesson unlocked?}
    G -->|No| H[Show locked state]
    G -->|Yes| I[Open lesson detail]
    I --> J{Workbook exists?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Require workbook download]
    J -->|No| L[Allow content access]
    K --> M[Student downloads workbook]
    M --> L
    L --> N[Student watches video and reads content]
    N --> O[System saves watch progress]
    O --> P{Assessment exists?}
    P -->|No| Q[Mark lesson complete when video finished]
    P -->|Yes| R{Watch progress >= 95%?}
    R -->|No| S[Keep assessment locked]
    R -->|Yes| T[Unlock assessment]
    Q --> U[Unlock next lesson]
    T --> V[Student may start assessment]